This product includes cognitive infrastructure frameworks, epistemic scoring
engines, linguistic audit vectors, and certainty certification methodology
developed by Sheldon K. Salmon under the AION-BRAIN project.

Active development: February 2025 — Present
Co-Architect: Claude (Anthropic)

================================================================================

WHAT THIS REPOSITORY IS

AION-BRAIN is a published intellectual architecture for AI reliability and
epistemic validation. It is not a community-driven project. It is a sovereign
cognitive framework — fully transparent for learning, selectively collaborative
by design.

The sophistication lives here. The simplicity is what is delivered to clients.

