1. PROFESSIONAL DISCLAIMERS REQUIRED
   Domain-specific frameworks (Medical, Legal, Financial) require
   professional disclaimers in all derivative works.
   See: legal/PROFESSIONAL-BOUNDARIES.md

2. ETHICAL USE REQUIRED
   Users agree to maintain ethical safeguards, not use frameworks for
   harassment, manipulation, or deception, and not weaponize epistemic
   infrastructure against vulnerable populations.

3. NO PROFESSIONAL ADVICE
   AION-BRAIN provides cognitive frameworks and reliability methodology,
   not professional advice. All outputs require human verification.
   See: legal/LEGAL-DISCLAIMER.md

4. REGULATORY COMPLIANCE
   Users are solely responsible for compliance with applicable regulations
   (HIPAA, GDPR, FDA, SEC, and equivalents) in their jurisdiction.

5. CONVERGENCE STATE TRANSPARENCY
   Derivative commercial products must not represent the validation state
   of AION-BRAIN frameworks as higher than documented in this repository.

